OL,3,C'A film about Leicester City's journey
OL,4,Ccould be a fairytale, comedy or
OL,5,Ctragedy'
OL,7,FRishi Khiroya and his family are life-
OL,8,Flong fans and have experienced the
OL,9,Femotional rollercoaster of the last
OL,10,Ffew years.
OL,12,FA Leicester City fan has described the
OL,13,Funique experience of following the
OL,14,Fclub.
OL,16,FLeicester City has been relegated from
OL,17,Fthe Championship after a 2-2 draw
OL,18,Fagainst Hull City and follows a run of
OL,19,Fonly one win in their last 16 games.
