OL,3,C'A film about Leicester City's journey
OL,4,Ccould be a fairytale, comedy or
OL,5,Ctragedy'
OL,7,FHe says if a film was made about the
OL,8,Fclub's journey, it would be a genre
OL,9,Fbuster - it could be a comedy, tragedy
OL,10,For a fairytale.
OL,12,FHe reckons that if you asked Leicester
OL,13,Ffans about relegation to League One in
OL,14,Fexchange for their Premier League
OL,15,Ftriumph, challenging in Europe and FA
OL,16,FCup success, they would take it.
